name: ChattyCat
0:
”Alexa, open Chatty Cat.”
”How are you?”
”You are so cute.”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: chatty cat
des: This skill will listen to what you say and will respond with different cat sounds. I built this skill so my kids could pretend that we still had a cat in the house. Speak to the Chatty Cat like she's your pet and listen to how she responds. I hope you enjoy using this skill. Icon illustrator Taniel Harvey (c)2018
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
